de: Amendment No 3 to Project Agreement between the Government of the Republic of Albania represented by the Council of Ministers of the Republic of Albania and the Albanian Power Corporation "KESH" and the Swiss Confederation represented by the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of the Federal Department of Economic Affairs, Education and Research on the Granting of Financial Assistance for the Dam Safety Project at the Drin and Mat River Cascades  - 21-07-2017 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und Albanien, vertreten durch den Ministerrat und der Albanischen Energiegesellschaft KESH, betreffend das Projekt «Staudamm Sicherheit»
en: Amendment No 3 to Project Agreement between the Government of the Republic of Albania represented by the Council of Ministers of the Republic of Albania and the Albanian Power Corporation "KESH" and the Swiss Confederation represented by the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of the Federal Department of Economic Affairs, Education and Research on the Granting of Financial Assistance for the Dam Safety Project at the Drin and Mat River Cascades  - 21-07-2017 - Project Agreement between the Government of the Swiss Confederation and the Council of Ministers of the Republic of Albania and the Albanian Power Corporation KESH on the Granting of Financial Assistance for the Dam Safety Project at the Drin and Mat River Cascades
fr: Amendment No 3 to Project Agreement between the Government of the Republic of Albania represented by the Council of Ministers of the Republic of Albania and the Albanian Power Corporation "KESH" and the Swiss Confederation represented by the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of the Federal Department of Economic Affairs, Education and Research on the Granting of Financial Assistance for the Dam Safety Project at the Drin and Mat River Cascades  - 21-07-2017 - Accord entre la Suisse, représentée par le SECO, et l'Albanie, représentée par le Conseil des ministres et la Société énergétique albanaise KESH, concernant le projet «sécurité des barrages»
